The Spanish Prisoner;;1997;;PG;;Drama,Mystery,Thriller;;7.2;;David Mamet;;Steve Martin,Ben Gazzara,Campbell Scott,Ricky Jay,Rebecca Pidgeon,Richard L. Friedman,Jerry Graff,G. Roy Levin,Hilary Hinckle,David Pittu,Christopher Kaldor,Felicity Huffman,Gary McDonald,Mike Robinson,Olivia Tecosky,Charlotte Potok,Paul Butler,J.J. Johnston;;Joe Ross has developed a process that will make his company a fortune. It will also make whoever has it a fortune, so the details are kept secret and secure. However, the executives at the company seem reluctant to commit to bonuses or royalties for Ross, so he starts looking at his options. He also has a new friend, the wealthy Jimmy Dell, and he is happy to give him advice on the matter.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120176/